kubectl port-forward -n monitoring svc/prometheus-kube-prometheus-prometheus 9090:9090


Access at: http://localhost:9090

üìå Notes

These commands must run in a terminal window (they block until you stop them with Ctrl+C)

You can run them in the background or use tools like tmux or screen if needed

Let me know if you'd like to create a shell script for this or expose more services.


